<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.10.6">
<l>kāṉa veṇkuṅ kuraṅkum mucuvum paṭaiyā vaṭalarakkar</l>
<l>māṉa maḻittu niṉṟa veṉṟi yammā ṉeṉakkeṉṟum</l>
<l>tēṉum pālu mamutu māya tirumāl tirunāmam</l>
<l>nāṉuñ coṉṉēṉ namaru muraimiṉ namōnā rāyaṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I said the divine name of the lord of victory who was steadfast,</l>
<l rend="indent">destroying the might of the murderous demons</l>
<l>[Using] forest bears, monkeys, and langurs as an army,</l>
<l>Tirumāl who is always honey, milk, and nectar to me;</l>
<l>Friends, you, too, please say the Namō Nārāyaṇam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
